Class ResCloudletList

java.lang.Object
org.cloudbus.cloudsim.lists.ResCloudletList
public class ResCloudletList
extends java.lang.Object
ResCloudletList is a collection of operations on lists of ResCloudlets.

  • Method Details

    • getByIdAndUserId

      public static <T extends ResCloudlet> ResCloudlet getByIdAndUserId​(java.util.List<T> list, int cloudletId, int userId)
      Returns a given Cloudlet. This method needs a combination of Cloudlet Id and User Id because each Cloud Users might have exactly same Cloudlet Ids.
      Parameters:
      cloudletId - a Cloudlet Id
      userId - an User Id
      list - the list
      Returns:
      the Cloudlet.
      Throws:
      java.lang.IndexOutOfBoundsException - - if a Cloudlet with specified Id and user id is not in the list.

    • indexOf

      public static <T extends ResCloudlet> int indexOf​(java.util.List<T> list, int cloudletId, int userId)
      Finds the index of a Cloudlet inside the list. This method needs a combination of Cloudlet Id and User Id because each Cloud User might have exactly the same Cloudlet Id.
      Parameters:
      cloudletId - a Cloudlet Id
      userId - an User Id
      list - the list
      Returns:
      the index in this list of the first occurrence of the specified Cloudlet, or -1 if the list does not contain this Cloudlet.

    • move

      public static <T extends ResCloudlet> boolean move​(java.util.List<T> listFrom, java.util.List<T> listTo, T cloudlet)
      Move a ResCloudlet object from this linked-list into a specified one.
      Parameters:
      listFrom - the list from
      listTo - the list to
      cloudlet - the cloudlet
      Returns:
      true if the moving operation successful, otherwise return false
